					p <cms:editable name='story_text' type='text' group='story_group'>I moved to London in the late nineties as a young married woman. In the beginning, it was an exciting experience for both of us, however it wasn't long before my marriage was showing signs that something was wrong. I started feeling isolated and worried, and eventually I faced the inevitability of divorce.</cms:editable>
